title: Rego (D. Maria Emilia Acciaioly)
body: She belonged to an ancient and distinguished Madeiran family and passed away over 70 years ago. According to the information we could gather, she published a small volume of verses, the title of which is unknown to us. In "Flores da Madeira," one of her compositions is included. We know nothing more about her.

D. Maria Emilia Acciaioly: Belonged to an ancient and distinguished Madeiran family, deceased over 70 years ago
